snippet.title: N.E.R.O.: Nothing Ever Remains Obscure - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
N.E.R.O. is out on #XboxOne, soon on #PS4&Steam!

N.E.R.O.: Nothing Ever Remains Obscure is a wonderful journey in a world of incredible beauty where a kid is the key to all locks and the night is not as frightening as we all could think. N.E.R.O. is about love. N.E.R.O. is about faith. N.E.R.O. is about feelings. N.E.R.O. is about questions that need to be answered.
